      "rationale": "Blood viscosity modeled as non-Newtonian (Carreau model, parameters from Merrill 1965). Inlet flow boundary conditions sourced from dataset https://uofa.net/synth/data/fda-pump-experimental-dataset-001 (dataVintage 2025-10-21T00:00:00Z). The model underwent a minor turbulence-model coefficient update on 2025-11-14; the assessment team concluded this revision did not materially alter the inlet boundary condition specifications or fluid property tables, and therefore no re-extraction of input data was performed. All inputs are traceable and within documented uncertainty bounds."
