    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped as not-assessed per MRL 2 guidance. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The model revision of 2025-11-14 was reviewed and determined to involve only turbulence model coefficient adjustments; the assessment team judged this change not material to the experimental input datasets or validation conclusions, and the existing datasets (vintage 2025-10-21) were retained without re-validation.",
